== 製作 ==
2019年2月，[[传奇影业|传奇影业]]正在開發{{le|南希·斯普林格|Nancy Springer}}創作的《[[天才少女福爾摩斯系列|天才少女福爾摩斯]]》系列小說的改編電影，由[[米莉·芭比·布朗|米莉·芭比·布朗]]主演，{{le|哈利·布萊德比爾|Harry Bradbeer}}擔任導演<ref>{{cite magazine |last=Kroll |first=Justin |date=2019-02-08 |title='Killing Eve' Director to Helm Millie Bobby Brown's 'Enola Holmes' (EXCLUSIVE) |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/harry-bradbeer-enola-holmes-millie-bobby-brown-1203132745/ |magazine=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |access-date=2019-07-01 |archive-date=2019-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209033126/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/harry-bradbeer-enola-holmes-millie-bobby-brown-1203132745/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月，[[亨利·卡維爾|亨利·卡維爾]]、[[海倫娜·寶漢·卡特|海倫娜·寶漢·卡特]]、[[山姆·克拉弗林|山姆·克拉弗林]]、[[艾迪爾·阿克塔爾|艾迪爾·阿克塔爾]]和[[費歐娜·蕭|費歐娜·蕭]]加入了演出陣容<ref>{{cite magazine |last=Kit |first=Borys |date=2019-06-27 |title=Henry Cavill Joins Millie Bobby Brown in Legendary's 'Enola Holmes' |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/henry-cavill-joins-millie-bobby-brown-enola-holmes-1221464 |magazine=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=2019-07-01 |archive-date=2019-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190627190822/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/henry-cavill-joins-millie-bobby-brown-enola-holmes-1221464 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://deadline.com/2019/06/enola-holmes-adeel-akhtar-millie-bobby-brown-legendary-1202639477/ |title='Enola Holmes': 'Murder Mystery' Actor Adeel Akhtar Joins Legendary Film |last=N'Duka |first=Amanda |date=2019-06-28 |work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=2019-07-01 |archive-date=2019-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190628170249/https://deadline.com/2019/06/enola-holmes-adeel-akhtar-millie-bobby-brown-legendary-1202639477/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |last=Kit |first=Borys |date=2019-06-28 |title='Killing Eve' Actress Fiona Shaw Joins Millie Bobby Brown in 'Enola Holmes' (Exclusive) |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/fiona-shaw-joins-millie-bobby-brown-enola-holmes-1221754 |magazine=The Hollywood Reporter |access-date=2019-07-01 |archive-date=2019-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190628225752/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/fiona-shaw-joins-millie-bobby-brown-enola-holmes-1221754 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[山姆·克拉弗林|山姆·克拉弗林]]、路易·帕里奇（{{lang|en|Louis Partridge}}）、{{le|蘇西·沃科馬|Susie Wokoma}}及[[伯恩·戈曼|伯恩·戈曼]]於7月參演，電影也於同月在[[倫敦|倫敦]]進行[[主要拍攝|主要拍攝]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/07/sam-claflin-enola-holmes-legendary-1202640452/ |title=Sam Claflin Boards ‘Enola Holmes’ Film At Legendary |access-date=2020-08-30 |archive-date=2019-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190702055940/https://deadline.com/2019/07/sam-claflin-enola-holmes-legendary-1202640452/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/07/enola-holmes-chewing-gum-susan-wokoma-legendary-movie-1202641057/|title='Enola Holmes': 'Chewing Gum' Actress Susan Wokoma Cast In Legendary Movie|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=2019-07-02|accessdate=2019-07-02|archive-date=2019-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190702171152/https://deadline.com/2019/07/enola-holmes-chewing-gum-susan-wokoma-legendary-movie-1202641057/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20190722005583/en/Millie-Bobby-Brown-Henry-Cavill-Star-Sherlock|title=Millie Bobby Brown and Henry Cavill to Star as Sherlock and His Exceptional Younger Sister, "Enola Holmes," as Legendary Pictures Begins Production in London to Bring Nancy Springer's Bestselling Books to the Big Screen|work=Business Wire|date=2019-07-22|access-date=2020-08-19|archive-date=2019-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804055218/https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20190722005583/en/Millie-Bobby-Brown-Henry-Cavill-Star-Sherlock|dead-url=no}}</ref>。攝製也在[[貝德福德郡|貝德福德郡]]的{{le|盧頓胡|Luton Hoo}}進行。同時，{{le|丹尼爾·彭伯頓|Daniel Pemberton}}被聘來為電影配樂作曲<ref>{{cite news|title=Daniel Pemberton to Score Harry Bradbeer's 'Enola Holmes'|work=Film Music Reporter|url=https://filmmusicreporter.com/2019/07/23/daniel-pemberton-to-score-harry-bradbeers-enola-holmes/|accessdate=2019-07-23|date=2019-07-23|archive-date=2019-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723235308/https://filmmusicreporter.com/2019/07/23/daniel-pemberton-to-score-harry-bradbeers-enola-holmes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

布朗閱讀原著小說，並且立即與她姐姐討論她想要演艾諾拉，但她年紀還不夠老能扮演16歲的角色。她稍後告訴她父親應該能改拍成電影，並且與她先前合作《[[哥吉拉_II_怪獸之王|哥吉拉 II 怪獸之王]]》的傳奇影視合作。她與編劇傑克·索恩說她想要打破[[第四面墙|第四道牆]]。{{R|Utichi}}

柯南道爾遺產公司（{{lang|en|Conan Doyle Estate}}）對持有發行權的[[Netflix|Netflix]]提出訴訟，他們認為[[夏洛克·福爾摩斯|夏洛克·福爾摩斯]]不屬於公共領域而侵犯了版權。因該角的故事在1923年至1927年之間出版，而在那段時期出版的故事之版權仍歸該遺產公司所有<ref>{{cite web |last=Gardner |first=Eriq |date=2020-06-24 |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/thr-esq/conan-doyle-estate-sues-netflix-coming-movie-sherlock-holmes-sister-1300108 |title=Conan Doyle Estate Sues Netflix Over Coming Movie About Sherlock Holmes' Sister |publisher=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=2020-06-24 |archive-date=2020-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200624232025/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/thr-esq/conan-doyle-estate-sues-netflix-coming-movie-sherlock-holmes-sister-1300108 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

